### Training

python run_summarization.py --mode=train --data_path=/home/siddiki/Text/finished_files/chunked/train_* --vocab_path=/home/siddiki/Text/finished_files/vocab --log_root=/home/siddiki/Logs/ --exp_name=myexperiment


### Evaluation

python run_summarization.py --mode=eval --data_path=/home/siddiki/Text/finished_files/chunked/val_* --vocab_path=/home/siddiki/Text/finished_files/vocab --log_root=/home/siddiki/Logs/ --exp_name=myexperiment


### Decoding

python run_summarization.py --mode=decode --data_path=/home/siddiki/Text/finished_files/chunked/val_* --vocab_path=/home/siddiki/Text/finished_files/vocab --log_root=/home/siddiki/Logs/ --exp_name=myexperiment


### Attention Visualizer (Needs Python3 Installed)

Clone this repo: https://github.com/abisee/attn_vis

Replace attn_vis_data.json with your own file.

Then in Terminal: python3 -m http.server 8000

Then, open new tab with:

http://localhost:8000/

